<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国 - 南华早报</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/rss/4/feed</link><description>来自中国的最新突发新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 02:01:21 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>最新报告称，中国不断增长的数据中心和人工智能产业可能会给稀缺的水资源带来压力</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3259230/chinas-growing-data-centres-and-ai-industry-could-strain-scarce-water-resources-according-new-report?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>香港智库表示，到 2030 年，中国数据设施的年用水量（其中近一半位于干旱地区）可能会增加一倍以上，而人工智能聊天机器人则“饮用大量的水”来冷却自己。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 02:00:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3259230/chinas-growing-data-centres-and-ai-industry-could-strain-scarce-water-resources-according-new-report?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>随着出口增长，中国在“数字丝绸之路”论坛上强调阿里巴巴和Shein在促进跨境电子商务方面的作用</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3259236/china-plays-alibaba-sheins-role-promoting-cross-border-e-commerce-digital-silk-road-forum-exports?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在西安举行的数字丝绸之路发展论坛上，阿里巴巴和Shein因帮助推动中国蓬勃发展的跨境电子商务行业而受到赞扬。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 01:00:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3259236/china-plays-alibaba-sheins-role-promoting-cross-border-e-commerce-digital-silk-road-forum-exports?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国GDP：第一季度增长“粉碎”预期，但北京是否在篮子里放了太多鸡蛋？</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/economic-indicators/article/3259182/china-gdp-first-quarter-growth-smashes-expectations-has-beijing-put-too-many-eggs-its-basket?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国今年前三个月备受关注的国内生产总值(GDP)数据超出预期，但3月份零售销售增速下降，第一季度房地产投资下降9.5%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 23:00:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/economic-indicators/article/3259182/china-gdp-first-quarter-growth-smashes-expectations-has-beijing-put-too-many-eggs-its-basket?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>广交会：订单激增，中国新能源出口企业热闹非凡，贸易限制威胁隐现</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3259206/canton-fair-chinas-new-energy-exporters-abuzz-orders-swell-threat-trade-curbs-looms?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>随着订单的增加，广交会上新能源设备的买家和参展商表现出无限的乐观情绪，但美国和欧盟可能采取的针对该行业的措施可能会破坏这一乐趣。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 22:00:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3259206/canton-fair-chinas-new-energy-exporters-abuzz-orders-swell-threat-trade-curbs-looms?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中美高级官员就“工业产能过剩”和反洗钱问题举行会谈</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3259255/senior-us-and-chinese-officials-hold-talks-industrial-overcapacity-and-anti-money-laundering?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>财政部长珍妮特·耶伦出席北京和华盛顿经济金融工作组第四次会议的交流活动。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 21:45:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3259255/senior-us-and-chinese-officials-hold-talks-industrial-overcapacity-and-anti-money-laundering?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰总统泽连斯基感谢德国总统肖尔茨对华外交</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/world/russia-central-asia/article/3259254/ukraines-volodymyr-zelensky-thanks-germanys-olaf-scholz-diplomacy-china?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>乌克兰总统表示，中国可以在确保结束战争方面发挥作用，并寻求北京支持在瑞士举行的和平峰会。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 21:31:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/world/russia-central-asia/article/3259254/ukraines-volodymyr-zelensky-thanks-germanys-olaf-scholz-diplomacy-china?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>美国国会小组报告称中国正在补贴全球芬太尼供应</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3259253/china-subsidising-global-fentanyl-supply-says-report-us-congressional-panel?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>专家作证说，尽管乔·拜登和习近平在 11 月就解决这种致命药物问题达成了协议，但几乎没有证据表明中国致力于这一努力，也没有看到太多成果。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 20:21:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3259253/china-subsidising-global-fentanyl-supply-says-report-us-congressional-panel?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>高级贸易特使表示，美国对价值超过3000亿美元的中国进口商品的关税审查即将完成</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3259252/us-tariffs-review-over-us300-billion-worth-chinese-imports-almost-done-says-top-trade-envoy?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>拜登政府“认真审视”现有工具，以有效应对北京政策造成的“依赖和脆弱性”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 20:00:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3259252/us-tariffs-review-over-us300-billion-worth-chinese-imports-almost-done-says-top-trade-envoy?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中美防长两年多来首次通话</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3259247/us-chinese-defence-chiefs-talk-first-time-more-two-years?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>劳埃德·奥斯汀国务卿与去年12月被任命为国防部长的董军上将之间的视频通话是美中关系解冻的最新迹象。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 15:45:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3259247/us-chinese-defence-chiefs-talk-first-time-more-two-years?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国GDP增长超出预期——为何分析师和商业团体仍持悲观态度？</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3259224/chinas-gdp-growth-beat-expectations-so-why-are-analysts-and-business-groups-still-downbeat?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>尽管第一季度GDP数据显示中国正在实现全年经济增长目标，但政策制定者仍被要求提振需求并推出更强有力的政策支持。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 15:00:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3259224/chinas-gdp-growth-beat-expectations-so-why-are-analysts-and-business-groups-still-downbeat?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国最高外交官王毅出访印度尼西亚、柬埔寨和巴布亚新几内亚，推动一带一路</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3259235/chinas-top-diplomat-wang-yi-push-belt-and-road-during-visits-indonesia-cambodia-and-papua-new-guinea?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>随着北京在美国的竞争中加强与东南亚的外交，外交部长王毅将于本周访问这三个国家。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 13:52:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3259235/chinas-top-diplomat-wang-yi-push-belt-and-road-during-visits-indonesia-cambodia-and-papua-new-guinea?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>巴黎奥运会：俄罗斯、以色列世界舆论分歧之际，法国马克龙呼吁中国帮助实施为期三周的“奥运休战”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3259238/paris-games-frances-macron-calls-china-help-3-week-olympic-truce-russia-israel-divide-world-opinion?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>分析人士表示，无论如何，中国长期以来一直呼吁停火，而任何明确谴责俄罗斯的要求都可能会失败。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 13:51:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3259238/paris-games-frances-macron-calls-china-help-3-week-olympic-truce-russia-israel-divide-world-opinion?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>由于传统芯片的主导地位日益增强，中国第一季度半导体产量跃升40%</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/tech-war/article/3259221/chinas-semiconductor-output-jumps-40-first-quarter-amid-growing-dominance-legacy-chips?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>研究人员表示，美国的出口管制可能会无意中导致中国在全球传统芯片生产中占据主导地位。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 13:30:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/tech-war/article/3259221/chinas-semiconductor-output-jumps-40-first-quarter-amid-growing-dominance-legacy-chips?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>IMF因“房地产行业陷入困境”而维持中国2024年GDP增​​长预期不变</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3259201/imf-keeps-chinas-2024-gdp-growth-estimate-unchanged-troubled-property-sector?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在中国第一季度GDP增长数据公布后，国际货币基金组织表示，缺乏“全面应对措施”可能会导致今年的经济增长低于北京方面的预期。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 13:00:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3259201/imf-keeps-chinas-2024-gdp-growth-estimate-unchanged-troubled-property-sector?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>百度声称 Ernie 聊天机器人拥有 2 亿用户，这表明生成式人工智能投资正在获得回报</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/tech-trends/article/3259205/baidu-claims-200-million-users-ernie-chatbot-sign-generative-ai-investments-are-paying?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>百度首席执行官李彦宏表示，随着中国人工智能竞赛的升温，百度的人工智能聊天机器人 Ernie Bot 已吸引了超过 2 亿用户。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 12:30:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/tech-trends/article/3259205/baidu-claims-200-million-users-ernie-chatbot-sign-generative-ai-investments-are-paying?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item></channel></rss>